src="/tpg/person/fair/smallfair.gif"  alt="Return to Fair Labor Standards
Handbook Home Page"></a> <a
href="/tpg/prices/personnelprices.html"><img src="/tpg/orderbut.gif" alt=" [
ORDER ]
"></a>
</pre>
</center>
