<Title>Section 504 Compliance Handbook Agency Chapters</Title> <P>

<body background="/tpg/gif/tpgpattern.gif> 
<center><IMG SRC="/tpg/fed_gts/hand/handhead.gif" alt="Section 504 Compliance
Handbook"></center></IMG><P>

<h2> Section 504 Compliance Handbook Agency Chapters</h2>

<body>
In addition to the <i>Section 504 Compliance Handbook</i>, agency chapters are available
providing in-depth discussions of rules issued by 22 federal funding agencies.
<P>

Each chapter discusses section 504 requirements specific to the funding agency
and includes the section 504 rules issued by the agency. With your <i>Handbook</i>
subscription, you may order as many of the following chapters as you need for a
complete section 504 compliance picture. Agency chapters are available for
the:<P>

<UL>
<LI>Corporation for National and Community Service<P>

<LI>Department of Agriculture<P>

<LI>Department of Commerce<P>

<LI>Department of Defense<P>

<LI>Department of Education requirements for postsecondary education<P>

<LI>Department of Education requirements for preschool, elementary and secondary
education<P>

<LI>Department of Energy<P>

<LI>Environmental Protection Agency<P>

<LI>General Services Administration<P>

<LI>Department of Health and Human Services<P>

<LI> Housing &amp; Urban Development<P>

<LI>Department of the Interior<P>

<LI>Department of Justice<P>

<LI>Department of Labor<P>

<LI>Legal Services Corporation<P>

<LI>National Endowment for the Arts<P>

<LI>National Endowment for the Humanities<P>

<LI>National Science Foundation<P>

<LI>Small Business Administration<P>

<LI>Department of State<P>

<LI>Department of Transportation<P>

<LI>Department of Veterans Affairs</UL><P>

The agency chapters may not be purchased separately, but only in addition to the
<i>Handbook</i>. Each chapter costs $35. For ordering information about the <i>Handbook</i>,
return to the <i>Section 504 Compliance Handbook</i> home page and double-click on
"Ordering Information."<P>



</body> <foot>

