src="/tpg/pen_ben/cobs/smallcobs.gif"  alt="Return to Coordination of Benefits
Handbook 
Home Page"></a> <a
href="/tpg/prices/benefitprices.html"><img src="/tpg/orderbut.gif" alt=" [ ORDER
]
"></a>
</pre>
</center>
