<html> <head>
<title>ANS Membership Form: Understanding Payment Options</title>
</head>

<body background="/graphics/gifs/logo.bkgrnd.gif">
<center>
<h3>ANS On-line Publications Ordering</h3>
<h1>Understanding Payment Options</h1>
<p>
<img src="/graphics/gifs/stripe.gif">
<p>
<table width=600><tr><td>
There are currently a number of available options to pay for your
on-line ANS Publications order.  In all cases, after filling out the
on-line order form and indicating your payment option and you
will receive a confirmation number.  This number will be important in
all the payment options.
<dl>
  <dt> <b>Direct Credit Card Payment</b>
  <dd> <blink><b>THIS IS NOT A SECURE SERVER!</b></blink> For those
       people who are of the valid opinion that sending their credit
       card info over the internet is no more dangerous than giving
       the card to a restaurant waiter for 10 minutes or reading it
       over a normal phone line, it is possible to enter the
       type, number, and expiry date directly on the form and complete
       your transaction.
       <p>
  <dt> <b>Telephone/Fax Credit Card Payment</b>
  <dd> You can either phone <i><b>1-800-NUCLEUS</b></i> and leave
       your name, credit card information, and confirmation
       number,<p>
       <i>OR</i><p>
       Fax your name, credit card info and confirmation number to
       <b><i>(708)352-0499</i></b>.
       <p>

  <dt> <b>Cheque or Money Order</b>
  <dd> Send a cheque or money order in U.S. Funds and indicating your
       confirmation number to:<p>

       <blockquote><blockquote>American Nuclear Society<br>
       P.O. Box 72475<br>
       Chicago, Illinois 60678-2475<br>
       USA</blockquote></blockquote>
       <p>

  <dt> <b>Wire Transfer</b>
  <dd> Wire transfer funds to:<p>

       <blockquote><blockquote>Account No. 824941<br>
       American National Bank<br>
       33 N. LaSalle St.<br>
       Chicago, IL 60690<br>
       USA</blockquote></blockquote>
</dl>
<p>
<img src="/graphics/gifs/stripe.gif">
<p>

In all cases, you will receive an e-mail from ANS Staff once your
payment has been received using your confirmation number to indicate
that your order is being processed.
</td>
</tr>
</table>

<img src="/graphics/gifs/stripe.gif">
<table width=600>
  <tr>
    <td valign=middle><a href="/"><img src="/graphics/gifs/atom.t.gif"
align=left>Return to<br>Home Page</a></td>
    <td align=center><address><a href="/guild">ANS Webweavers' Guild</a>
<a href="mailto:wg-chair@ans.neep.wisc.edu">&lt;wg-chair@ans.neep.wisc.edu&gt;</a></address></td>
  </tr>
</table>

