<html> <head>
<title>ANS-WG Current Contributors</title>
</head>

<body background="/graphics/gifs/logo.bkgrnd.gif">
<center>
<table width=600><tr><td>
<center><h1>Current Contributors of the ANS Webweavers' Guild</h1></center>
<p><img src="/graphics/gifs/stripe.gif"><p>

The following people have contributed to the HTML/CGI development of
<i>The ANSWER</i>, the official WWW resource of the American Nuclear
Society.

<ul>
  <li> <a href="http://maple.fzk.de/~wilson/">Paul Wilson</a>, ANS-WG
       Chair and primary developer
  <li> <a href="http://www.cannon.net/~gonyeau/nuclear/index.htm">Joseph
       Gonyeau</a>, primary developer of
       <a href="http://www.cannon.net/~gonyeau/ans/news.html"><i>The
       ANSWER</i> News Wire</a>.
  <li> <a href="http://rainbow.rmii.com/~jgraham/">John Graham</a>,
       primary developer of <a href="http://rainbow.rmii.com/~jgraham/The.ANSWER/International/International.html">International section</a>
</ul>

</table>

<img src="/graphics/gifs/stripe.gif">
