__ Non-smoking         -- Smoking             __ Accessible

</pre>

<font size=-1>Rooms are subject to 13% tax plus $1.50 per room
occupancy tax.  One night's deposit or credit card information must
accompany reservation to guarantee room.  (One night will be billed to
your credit card.) Reservations must be received by October 21, 1996.
After this date, reservations are subject to availability.  Deposits
are refundable if reservation is cancelled 72 hours prior to arrival.
<b>If departure date is changed to an earlier date after check-in, a
$35 charge will be assessed.</b> NOTE: RESERVE YOUR ROOM EARLY.  You
will receive written confirmation of your reservation from the
hotel.</font>

