<center>
<h3>ANS TOPICAL MEETING</h3>
<h1>DD&amp;R, What Does it Mean?</h1>
</center>
<p>
<img src=/graphics/gifs/stripe.gif>
<p>

<a name="monpm"><center><h3>Monday, November 11</h3></center></a>
<dl>
  <dt>  <i>1:00 p.m.</i>
  <dd>
       <dl>
	 <dt> <i><b>DD&amp;R Plenary: Planning and Conducting DD&amp;R Projects to Benefit Mankind</b></i><br>
	      sponsored by DDRD.<br>
	      Session organizer: Rich Ranellone (Tenneco NNS).<br>
	      All invited
	 <dd> Panelists:
	      <ul>
		<li> Andrew Kadak (YAEC, Bolton)
		<li> Robert Lallement (CEA-France)
		<li> Michio Ichikawa (JAERI-Japan)
		<li> Stephen Warren (DOE)
	      </ul>
       </dl>
</dl>

<p>
<img src=/graphics/gifs/stripe.gif>
<p>

<a name="tuesam"><center><h3>Tuesday, November 12</h3></center></a>
<dl>
  <dt> <i>8:30 a.m.</i>
  <dd> 
       <dl>
	 <dt> <i><b>Limitations in Measuring Background as Part of Decommissioning/Recycling-Panel	</b></i><br>
	      sponsored by DDRD.<br>
	      Session organizer: Andrew Wallo III (DOE).<br>
	      All invited.
	 <dd> Senior-level speakers invited from government agencies, national laboratories, and industry.
	     <p>

	 <dt> <i><b>Transportation and Packaging of DD&amp;R Materials</b></i><br>
	      sponsored by DDRD.<br>
	      Session organizer: Erich Opperman (Westinghouse SRC).
	 <dd>
	      <ul>
		<li> The Use of Sealed Intermodal Container for
		     Packagings for LSA and SCO, Robert A.. Vaughan
		     (Croft)
		<li> Shippingport Reactor Pressure Vessel Safety
		     Analysis Report for Packaging, Patrick C. Ferrell
		     (Westinghouse Hanford)
		<li> Radcalc: Transportation Packaging Software to
		     Determine Hydrogen Generation and Transportation
		     Classification, Janet R. Green, K. E. Hillesland,
		     V. E. Roetman, J. G. Field (Westinghouse Hanford)
		<li> Impact of Recent DOT Regulatory Changes (HM-169A)
		     on D&amp;D Packaging and Transportation, Don
		     A. Edling (Edling Assoc)
		<li> Decontamination and Disposal of Steam Generators,
		     George T. Hamilton, J. Radomicki (Hake Assoc),
		     C. Hultman (BNFL US, Fairfax), Mike Byrne (MSC,
		     Oak Ridge)
	      </ul>
	      <p>

	 <dt> <i><b>D&amp;D Technologies-I</b></i><br>
	      sponsored by DDRD.<br>
	      Session organizer: Samit K. Bhattacharyya (ANL).
	 <dd>
	      <ul>
		<li> Demonstration of D&amp;D Technologies by the Japan
		     Power Demonstration Reactor Decommissioning
		     Project, Satoshi Yanagihara (JAERI-Japan)
