		     CP-5 Reactor Large-Scale Demonstration Project,
		     D. Black (ANL)
		<li> Soil-Washing Technologies in Europe, H. Runge
		     (DETEC-Germany), D. Schmidt (Nukem, Columbia)
		<li> The NFS Decontamination and Volume Reduction
		     System (DVRS), S. Schutt (NFS)
		<li> Integrated Characterization Systems, R. Bernardi
		     (BIR)
		<li> D&amp;D Technology Development Activities at NUPEC,
		     N. Ogawa (NUPEC)
	      </ul>
	      <p>

	 <dt> <i><b>Benchmarking Decommissioning Costs</b></i><br>
	      sponsored by DDRD.<br>
	      Session organizer: Leo Lessard (YAEC).
	 <dd>
	      <ul>
		<li> What Goes Up Must Come Down? Not True for
		     Decommissioning Costs, Mary Fisher (Pub Svc
		     Colorado, Denver)
		<li> Yankee Nuclear Power Station-Analysis of
		     Decommissioning Costs, Leo P. Lessard (YAEC,
		     Bolton)
		<li> Benchmarking Transition Costs for the Fast Flux
		     Test Facility, Russell K. Hulvey (Westinghouse
		     Hanford)
