		     Research Facilities: Application to French CEA,
		     B. Serise, Y. Schwob (SGN-France),
		     J. G. Nokhamzon, M. Jacques (CEA-France)
		<li> Conducting D&amp;D Activities in a Fixed-Price
		     Environment, Jerry Ogg (Alaron)
		<li> The Total Cost to Decommission Shoreham, Edward
		     C. Abbott (ABZ)
		<li> Conceptual Engineering and Cost Estimates for the
		     D&amp;D of the Mound Plant Technical, Semi-Works, and
		     Research Buildings, J. Michael Usher (Parsons
		     Infrastructure &amp; Tech Group)
		<li> Benchmarking Cost Estimate; Trojan
		     Large-Component Removal Project, Thomas LaGuardia
		     (TLG Svs)
	      </ul>
       </dl>
       <a name="tuespm"><p></a>

  <dt> <i>1:00 p.m.</i>
  <dd>
       <dl>
	 <dt> <i><b>Privatization and Its Application at Federal Facilities-Panel	</b></i><br>
	      sponsored by DDRD.<br>
	      Session organizer: Dennis A. Bitz (Consult).
	 <dd> Senior-level speakers invited from financial institutions, and the law, business, and industrial communities.
	      <p>

	 <dt> <i><b>Commercial Facilities Decommissioning Experience (Domestic/International)</b></i><br>
	      sponsored by DDRD.<br>
	      Session organizer: Vince Likar (Westinghouse).
	 <dd>
	      <ul>
		<li> Fort St. Vrain Decommissioning Experience, Mary
		     J. Fisher (Pub Svc Colorado, Denver), Samuel
		     W. Chesnutt (Pub Svc Colorado, Platteville),
