	      sponsored by DDRD.<br>
	      Session organizer: Jerry Hyde (DOE).
	 <dd>
	      <ul>
		<li> Lessons Learned by Dismantling Two German BWRs in
		     Gundremmingen, Unit A (KRB), and Kahl (VAK),
