	 <dd>
	      <ul>
		<li> Nuclear Criticality Safety Modeling of an LEU
		     Deposit, M. Jonathan Haire, Karla R. Elam,
		     W. Curtis Jordan (ORNL), T. L. Dahl, Sr. (LMES)
