		     Demonstration Project, J. S. Bennion (Idaho State
		     Univ), R. D. Boston, A. S. Johnson (LMAES)
		<li> Destruction of Highly Enriched Uranium Fuel
		     Manufacturing Building Under Criticality Control,
		     Richard S. Kingsley (B&amp;W NES)
		<li> Areal Density Application to U-Contaminated CaF2
		     Storage, Lon E. Paulson (GENE)
		<li> Criticality Issues in Decommissioning Activities
		     at Sellafield, Stephen J. Walls, Neil Harris
		     (BNFL-UK)
		<li> Cleanup of the Most Dangerous Facility, Building
		     771, at Rocky Flats, H. Toffer, J.L. Byrd,
		     H.F. Larum, R.E. Wilson (SSC)
	      </ul>
       </dl>
</dl>
