	 <center><h1>Generate Registration Form and Script</h1>
	 <img src=/graphics/gifs/stripe.gif></center>

	 This form should help you generate an on-line form to allow
	 registration for your conference or meeting.  Simply fill out
	 the data below, and submit this form.  When the results
	 appear, use your browser to save them as a file with the
	 appropriate name.  At the same time, the script necessary to
	 process your form will be automagically created and sent to
	 the ANS Webweavers' Guild.  You are therefore encouraged not
	 to change the form once you have saved it.

	 <p><img src=/graphics/gifs/stripe.gif><p>

	 <form method="POST" action="gen.reg.form.cgi">
	 <center><h3>About You</h3></center>

	 To ensure that errors and problems can be debugged, please
	 tell me something about you and your site.  If you already
	 know the final URL for the registration form on your site,
	 please use it below.  Otherwise, use the URL for whatever
	 information already exists for your meeting.

	 <table width=100%>
	   <tr align=center>
	     <td> <input name="name" size="30"><br>
		  <i>Your Full Name</i>
		  </td>
	     <td> <input name="email" size="30"><br>
		  <i>Your e-mail address</i>
		  </td>
	   </tr>
	   <tr align=center>
	     <td colspan=2> <input name="url" size="60"><br>
		  URL for this meeting and/or this form
		  </td>
	   </tr>
         </table>
	 	 
	 <p><img src=/graphics/gifs/stripe.gif><p>

	 <center><h3>About the Event</h3></center>

	 <table width=100%>
