<HEAD>
   <TITLE>ANS Exec Conference Wednesday Program</TITLE>
   <META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Mozilla/3.01Gold (Win95; I) [Netscape]">
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="/graphics/gifs/logo.bkgrnd.gif">

<CENTER><TABLE WIDTH="600" >
<TR>
<TD>
<H3 ALIGN=CENTER>ADVANCE PROGRAM &amp; MEETING REGISTRATION</H3>

<H3 ALIGN=CENTER>ANS EXECUTIVE CONFERENCE</H3>

<H3 ALIGN=CENTER><I>Decommissioning and Spent Fuel Disposal</I></H3>

<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>Wednesday, April 30, 1997</H1>

<P><IMG SRC="/graphics/gifs/stripe.gif" HEIGHT=3 WIDTH=600></P>

<H3 ALIGN=CENTER>7:30 am - 4:30 pm</H3>

<CENTER><P><B>REGISTRATION</B></P></CENTER>

<H3 ALIGN=CENTER>8:00 am - 12:00 pm</H3>

<CENTER><P><B>MORNING SESSION </B></P></CENTER>

<CENTER><P><B><I>&quot;Major Activities and Projects; Options, Challenges
and Solutions&quot; </I></B></P></CENTER>

<P>The obstacles faced and the problems solved in re-inventing and optimizing
major projects within decommissioning projects will be discussed. Although
there will be a focus on certain projects in the presentations, the speakers
and the group will be encouraged to think beyond the specific projects
and make the discussion much more global.</P>

<DL>
<DT>Session Chairman &amp; Coordinator:</DT>

<DD><B>R. Jon Stouky</B>, <I>President, Mega-Tech Services, Inc., Jamestown,
NC </I></DD>

<DT>Speakers: </DT>

<DL>
<DT><B>R. Jon Stouky</B>, <I>President, Mega-Tech Services, Inc., Jamestown,
NC </I></DT>

<DD>Mr. Stouky will discuss decommissioning low-level radioactive and mixed
waste management on-site and off-site options and benefits. </DD>

<DT><B>Charles W. Adey</B>, <I>Vice President, TTX Engineering, Plymouth,
MA</I> </DT>

<DD>Mr. Adey will discuss the industry experience in termination survey
programs and decommissioning cost management systems. </DD>

<DT><B>Russell A. Mellor</B>, <I>Manager of Operations &amp; Decommissioning
Manager, Yankee Atomic Electric Company, Bolton, MA </I></DT>

<DD>Mr. Mellor will discuss the Yankee Rowe experience with the one-piece
reactor vessel shipment project.</DD>

<DT><B>Steven B. Nichols</B>, <I>Manager, Decommissioning Projects, Portland
General Electric Company, Trojan Nuclear Power Plant, Rainier, OR </I></DT>

<DD>Mr. Nichols will discuss the Trojan Reactor Vessel and Internals One-Piece
Removal project. </DD>

<DT><B>Sam Bhattacharyya</B>, <I>Manager of Technology Development, Argonne
National Laboratory, Argonne, IL </I></DT>

<DD>Dr. Bhattacharryya will discuss the ANL and METC programs directed
at the development of decommissioning technologies, and the adaptation
of these technologies to DOE and commercial projects. </DD>
</DL>
</DL>

<H3 ALIGN=CENTER>12:00 pm - 1:30 pm </H3>

<CENTER><P><B>GROUP LUNCHEON</B></P></CENTER>

<H3 ALIGN=CENTER>1:30 pm - 4:30 pm </H3>

