<html><head><title>Nuke News, 12/3/96</title></head>

<body background="/graphics/gifs/logo.bkgrnd.gif">
<center>
<h1>Nuke News for 12/3/96</h1>
<h3>distributed by Charles Sayles</h3>
<a href="96.03.11.html">Previous Nuke News</a>
