... Commonwealth Edison Senior Vice President Thomas Maiman has been
named to oversee the utility's nuclear division, and Senior Vice
President Michael Wallace was named to direct critical strategic
nuclear business issues (CHICAGO SUN-TIMES, 4/12/96, p. 45, Staff
