<a name=11><b>Facts Being Distorted in Cold Fusion Controversy</b><br></a>
<i>Edmund Storms</i>

<a name=12><b>Response to ``Facts Being Distorted in Cold Fusion Controversy''</b><br></a>
<i>Lee D. Hansen, Steven E. Jones</i>
<p>

<a name=13><b>Response to ``Facts Being Distorted in Cold Fusion Controversy''</b><br></a>
<i>Nathan J. Hoffman</i>
<p>

<a name=14><b>Comments on ``Calorimetry, Excess Heat, and Faraday Efficiency in Ni-H<sub>2</sub>O Electrolytic Cells''</b><br></a>
<i>W. R. Good II</i>
<p>

<a name=15><b>Response to ``Comments on `Calorimetry, Excess Heat, and Faraday Efficiency in Ni-H<sub>2</sub>O Electrolytic Cells' ''</b><br></a>
<i>Z. Shkedi</i>


