<img src=/graphics/gifs/stripe.gif width=100%> <p>
<center><h3>CRITICAL REVIEW</h3></center>
<dl>
<a href="#0"><dt><b>Evolution and Status of D-<sup>3</sup>He Fusion: A Critical Review</b><br></a>
<dd><i>W. R. Fundamenski, A. A. Harms</i>
