<center><h1>REGULAR ISSUE CONTENTS</h1></center>
<center><h3>TECHNICAL PAPERS</h3></center>
<a href="#15"><dt><b>Thermal Fatigue Testing of a Diffusion-Bonded Beryllium Divertor Mock-Up Under ITER-Relevant Conditions</b><br></a>
<dd><i>Dennis L. Youchison, Radmir N. Guiniatouline, Robert D. Watson, Jimmie M. McDonald, David S. Walsh, V. I. Beloturov, Igor V. Mazul, Andrey P. Zakharov, Bernice E. Mills, Dale R. Boehme, Vladislav Ilich Savenko</i>
