<center><h3>DEPARTMENTS</h3></center>
<h5>Meeting Report</h5>
<dl>
  <dt><b>Summary of Seventh International Workshop on Carbon Materials, Stockholm, Sweden, September 21-22, 1995</b><br>
  <dd><i>M. Rubel</i>
       <p>
       
