<img src="/graphics/gifs/stripe.gif">
<p>

<center><h3>In the next issue:</h3></center>

The March 1997 issue will feature "The future of nuclear power,"
by Chauncey Starr, president emeritus of the Electric Power
Research Institute, "Nuclear power in a competitive environment:
Myths and facts," by Joe F. Colvin, president and CEO of the
Nuclear Energy Institute, an update on food irradiation, and the
latest World List of Nuclear Power Plants.

<p>
