<center><h3>TECHNICAL NOTE</h3></center>
</dl>
<h5>ENRICHMENT AND REPROCESSING SYSTEMS</h5>
<dl>
<a href="#9"><dt><b>Development of Pyrometallurgical Partitioning of Actinides from High-Level Radioactive Waste Using a Reductive Extraction Step</b><br></a>
<dd><i>Takatoshi Hijikata, Masahiro Sakata, Hajime Miyashiro, Kensuke Kinoshita, Tatsuhiro Higashi, Tadaharu Tamai</i>
