<p>
<img src="/graphics/gifs/stripe.gif" width=100%>
<p>

<center><h3>INTRODUCTION</h3></center>

<dl>
  <dt><b>Fusion Energy R&D and the European Fusion Programme---An Introduction to the 2nd Carolus Magnus Summer School</b>
  <dd><i>H. Bruhns</i>
       <p>

  <dt><b>Energy for Future Centuries---Will Fusion Be an Inexhaustible, Safe and Clean Energy Source?</b>
  <dd><i>G. Van Oost, J. P. H. E. Ongena</i>
       <p>
  <dt><b>Thermonuclear Burn Criteria</b>
  <dd><i>Gerd H. Wolf, Bernhard Unterberg</i>
</dl>

<p>
<img src="/graphics/gifs/stripe.gif" width=100%>
<p>

